A nice look back at the popular prime time musical variety show
(1964-1966) by many of those who were in it.  This special may
have been created to hype the Rhino Entertainment video of 
series highlights that was released later in 1991, and 1992.
Lots of very cool clips in this, but no complete performances.
Interesting recollections by many key players give insight to
this classic television program.

In order of appearance:
